item.title: Support
item.description: FAQ: ## Sign up options You may use email, facebook, or google logins For email, check the verification email sent. to get another verificaiton email, login with the email and password used to create an account and tap resend. For other enquiries, email: support@dealbasin.com

item.title: Privacy
